{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3fef935d98","title":"蒋介石已向我中原部队实行攻击","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1c34b2bbd7","index":0,"year":1946,"month":6,"day":27,"articleId":"3fef935d98"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fe8871d149","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石已向我中原部队实行攻击","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3fef935d98"},{"id":"51d24fd42d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年6月27日）周，并告刘、邓、薄，陈、舒，邓、张蒋介石所谓四十八小时后有惊人举动，是指阴谋歼灭我中原部头而言，蒋于月中下令聚齐有不许漏网之语。昨有起实行攻击，我中原部队不得不起而自卫。这一自卫斗争是否能不受严重损失，现尚不能预计。请对外广泛揭发国民党之阴课","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3fef935d98"},{"id":"ff1db36e60","type":"paragraph","text":"中火","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3fef935d98"},{"id":"a4fe1d03f5","type":"paragraph","text":"已感门[2]刘、邓、薄，招刘伯承、邓小平、薄一波，当时分别任晋莫鲁豫军区司令员、政治委员和第一到政治委员。陈、舒，指陈毅、舒同，当时分别任新四军军长兼山东军区司令员和或治部主任。邓、张，指邓子恢、张患丞，当时分别任华中军区政治委员和司令员。311946年6月26日，国民党蒋分石集团悍毅停战协定，大举围","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3fef935d98"}],"page":{"id":"9a68b44cbf","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3fef935d98","start":433,"end":433}}}},"__N_SSG":true}